<subSubSection id="31B26528F1503266C72ACDBA9B7A1FD9" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph id="791736A3F1503266C72ACDBA9B7A1FD9" blockId="21.[136,1451,160,223]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
Type (designated by Senghas &amp; Gerlach 1993b: 1698): 
<emphasis id="4BDCEAB1F1503266C1BCCDBA9DF11FBD" bold="true" box="[1160,1188,161,187]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">—</emphasis>
